### 14.2 论坛投票 MVP 验收建议顺序：
# 1. 先执行“发布带投票帖子”，从 responseData 复制帖子 ID 到 @ForumPoll_PostId
# 2. 再执行“获取带投票帖子的列表”和“获取带投票帖子详情”，确认列表只回轻量摘要、详情回完整 VoPoll
# 3. 执行“按帖子获取投票详情”，从返回结果中复制一个 optionId 到 @ForumPoll_OptionId
# 4. 执行“提交投票”与“重复提交投票（预期失败）”
# 5. 最后用预置的已截止帖子 ID 验证“截止后提交投票（预期失败）”

### 14.3 发布带投票帖子（成功路径）
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Post/Publish
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

{
  "title": "论坛投票 MVP 验收帖",
  "content": "用于串联论坛投票 MVP 验收：列表识别、详情展示、投票提交与失败语义。",
  "categoryId": 1,
  "tagNames": ["投票", "验收"],
  "poll": {
    "question": "今天午饭更想吃什么？",
    "endTime": "2030-03-13T18:00:00+08:00",
    "options": [
      {
        "optionText": "盖饭"
      },
      {
        "optionText": "面条"
      },
      {
        "optionText": "轻食",
        "sortOrder": 5
      }
    ]
  }
}

### 14.4 发布带重复投票选项的帖子（预期 400）
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Post/Publish
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

{
  "title": "论坛投票非法参数验收帖",
  "content": "用于验证发布阶段的投票参数校验。",
  "categoryId": 1,
  "tagNames": ["投票"],
  "poll": {
    "question": "重复选项是否会被拦截？",
    "options": [
      {
        "optionText": "奶茶"
      },
      {
        "optionText": "奶茶"
      }
    ]
  }
}

### 14.5 获取带投票帖子的列表（确认仅回轻量摘要）
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Post/GetList?keyword=论坛投票%20MVP%20验收帖&pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 14.6 获取带投票帖子详情（确认返回完整 VoPoll）
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Post/GetById/{{ForumPoll_PostId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 14.7 按帖子获取投票详情（用于复制 optionId）
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Poll/GetByPostId?postId={{ForumPoll_PostId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 14.8 提交投票（成功路径）
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Poll/Vote
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

{
  "postId": {{ForumPoll_PostId}},
  "optionId": {{ForumPoll_OptionId}}
}

### 14.9 重复提交投票（预期失败：你已经投过票）
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Poll/Vote
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

{
  "postId": {{ForumPoll_PostId}},
  "optionId": {{ForumPoll_OptionId}}
}

### 14.10 截止后提交投票（预期失败：投票已截止）
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Poll/Vote
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

{
  "postId": {{ForumPoll_ExpiredPostId}},
  "optionId": {{ForumPoll_ExpiredOptionId}}
}

### 14.11 论坛问答 MVP 验收建议顺序：
# 1. 先执行“发布问答帖”，从 responseData 复制帖子 ID 到 @ForumQuestion_PostId
# 2. 再执行“获取问答帖列表”和“获取问答帖详情”，确认列表回轻量问答摘要、详情回完整 VoQuestion
# 3. 执行“提交回答（成功路径）”，从返回的 VoAnswers 中复制 answerId 到 @ForumQuestion_AnswerId
# 4. 执行“提问者采纳回答（成功路径）”
# 5. 再执行“重复采纳（预期失败）”与“普通帖提交回答（预期失败）”

### 14.12 发布问答帖（成功路径）
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Post/Publish
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

{
  "title": "论坛问答 MVP 验收帖",
  "content": "用于串联论坛问答 MVP 验收：列表识别、详情展示、回答提交与提问者采纳。",
  "categoryId": 1,
  "tagNames": ["问答", "验收"],
  "isQuestion": true
}

### 14.13 获取问答帖列表（确认回轻量问答摘要）
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Post/GetList?keyword={{ForumQuestion_AnsweredKeyword}}&pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 14.14 获取问答帖详情（确认返回完整 VoQuestion）
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Post/GetById/{{ForumQuestion_PostId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 14.15 提交回答（成功路径）
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Question/Answer
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

{
  "postId": {{ForumQuestion_PostId}},
  "content": "先检查配置、连接串和日志输出，再定位具体异常。"
}

### 14.16 提问者采纳回答（成功路径）
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Question/Accept
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

{
  "postId": {{ForumQuestion_PostId}},
  "answerId": {{ForumQuestion_AnswerId}}
}

### 14.17 重复采纳回答（预期失败：当前问题已采纳答案）
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Question/Accept
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

{
  "postId": {{ForumQuestion_PostId}},
  "answerId": {{ForumQuestion_AnswerId}}
}

### 14.18 普通帖提交回答（预期失败：当前帖子不是问答帖）
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Question/Answer
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

{
  "postId": 1,
  "content": "普通帖不应允许走问答回答接口。"
}

